		"ItemTooltips"
		{
			"item_arcane_boots"		"Early mana boost. To be disassembled into Aether Lens and Phase Boots later on"
			"item_aether_lens"		"Increases Bane's manapool and effective catch up range"
			"item_phase_boots"		"Additional movement speed and armor are pretty much all Bane needs seems he doesn't need attack speed and stats more than he already has"
			"item_medallion_of_courage"		"Additional armor and utility. It will help with mana sustain and tankiness, but it will also help with damage output early on for a cheap price"
			"item_hand_of_midas"		"Good for cases when you won your lane early on, but can't finish the game early. Bane struggles with farming after laning stage, so it may be a helpful pickup"
			"item_yasha_and_kaya"		"You don't really need tankiness, and Yaha-Kaya may help you with both farming and damage output if you're going to establish your domination"
			"item_solar_crest"		"Natural upgrade to Medallion and useful buff for your team"
			"item_sheepstick"		"Reliable disable and mana sustain"
			"item_mjollnir"		"May be helpful with attack speed steal talent. Early Maelstrom may solve your farming issue and later on it may work great in combination with either frontline core or Bane's inbuilt tankiness"
			"item_ultimate_scepter"		"Great addition after picking up level 25 talent. It's not really worth picking up beforehand because it won't be as effective and it will leave you without mana anyway"
			"item_hurricane_pike"		"Addition for rightclick build"
			"item_guardian_greaves"		"Strong regen aura and useful item to have in general. Good pickup if you're playing more of an utility core and there's no better Greaves carrier on your team"
			"item_force_staff"		"Good thing to have against slows and similar stuff in its nature (X-Mark)"
			"item_lotus_orb"		"Against silences and purgable slows"
			"item_heavens_halberd"		"Against high attack damage cores"
			"item_pipe"		"Against magic heavy lineups"
			"item_glimmer_cape"		"Good item to save allies (or yourself) from being focused"
			"item_vladmir"		"In case nobody has Vlads"
			"item_greater_crit"		"In case you're going full core and lack a bit of damage"
			"item_shivas_guard"		"For a hybrid core way when you need armor"
			"item_sphere"		"Against strong single target disables (e.g. Doom)"
			"item_octarine_core"		"Nice addition for a hybrid core (getting use of Mjolnir cooldown reduction, mjolnir procs and reduced cooldown on Q and E)"
			"item_necronomicon"		"Farming solution, basically a midas replacement with mana regen. May be upgraded to get more damage during the ult"
			"item_soul_ring"		"Another mana solution, may replace Bracer, but it's more expensive as well"
			"item_blade_mail"		"Efficient stats, additional armor, active ability suitable for active tanky Bane"
			"item_spirit_vessel"		"You don't really need it yourself, but it's usually a strong team oriented item. You may consider dropping Solar Crest in favor of Spirit Vessel "
		}
